# SkillLink Platform — API Endpoints

## Authentication
- POST /api/v1/auth/register — register a new user
- GET /api/v1/auth/confirm-email — confirm email address
- POST /api/v1/auth/login — login and get JWT token
- POST /api/v1/auth/logout — logout and invalidate token
- POST /api/v1/auth/forgot-password — request password reset
- POST /api/v1/auth/reset-password — reset password with token

## Users
- GET /api/v1/users/profile — get current user profile
- PUT /api/v1/users/update/{user_id} — update user profile
- DELETE /api/v1/users/delete/{user_id} — delete user profile

## Files
- POST /api/v1/files/upload/avatar — upload user avatar
- GET /api/v1/files/get/avatar — get user avatar

## Specialists
- POST /api/v1/specialists/create — create specialist profile
- GET /api/v1/specialists/get/{specialist_id} — get specialist by id
- PUT /api/v1/specialists/update/{specialist_id} — update specialist profile
- PATCH /api/v1/specialists/deactivate/{specialist_id} — deactivate specialist
- DELETE /api/v1/specialists/delete/{specialist_id} — delete specialist
- PATCH /api/v1/specialists/verify/{specialist_id} — verify specialist
- GET /api/v1/specialists/search — search specialists

## Orders
- POST /api/v1/orders/create — create order
- GET /api/v1/orders/get/{order_id} — get order by id
- GET /api/v1/orders/my — get my orders
- GET /api/v1/orders/active — get active orders
- GET /api/v1/orders/specialist/my — get specialist orders
- PUT /api/v1/orders/update/{order_id} — update order
- POST /api/v1/orders/take/{order_id} — try to take order(creating request)
- POST /api/v1/orders/complete/{order_id} — complete order
- POST /api/v1/orders/cancel/{order_id} — cancel order
- DELETE /api/v1/orders/delete/{order_id} — delete order

## Catalog
- POST /api/v1/catalog/create — create catalog entry
- GET /api/v1/catalog/get/catalog/{specialist_id} — get specialist catalog
- PUT /api/v1/catalog/update/{catalog_id} — update catalog entry
- DELETE /api/v1/catalog/delete/{catalog_id} — delete catalog entry

## Requests
- GET /api/v1/requests/get/all/{user_id} — get all requests for user
- PUT /api/v1/requests/approve/{request_id} — approve request
